title: SPIRAL (SAW Sequel) Trailer 2 Thoughts and Discussion
author: Reel Talk
comment: Just the YouTuber I wanted to see, Spiral is looking bloody horrifying and I can’t wait for the new traps to be revealed!
I want the Bathroom back!!! The most iconic element in the whole franchise imho! And I want simple mechanical traps, not too big and spectacular
I think the killer is the Police Captain. I can't remember the actresses' name, but yeah. The reason is that the voice, even though it has been modulated, still sounds femine.
The new trailer has really brought out my inner Saw fan!
Hoffman didn't need previously recorded tapes to achieve John Kramer's voice. Albeit it sounded a tiny bit modulated it was unmistakeably Jigsaw.
